default1.1
default              
defaultPassenger transport is a service to people, to facilitate fulfilled lives when no other means of mobility is available.
default1.2
default              
defaultPassengers do not live and work within neat administrative boundaries.
default1.3
default              
defaultServices in major transport modes have to be compatible with life needs - to and from work, reaching shops, markets
default,
default civic duties, leisure activities etc.
default1.4
default              
defaultNot everyone has online facilities, or if they do 
defaultmay not
default use them effectively.  
defaultNot everyone has credit / debit facilities to make online purchases.
default1.5
default              
defaultIntegration of different service modes is vital to enable complex journeys.
