defaultis under-writing
default an extra vehicle on that route 
defaultby a
default sole operator.  Service planners work for an employer, not passengers, apart from remaining municipal bus operators.  This gives the bus company an opportunity for a new bus for nothing or very little, as the funding authority will 
defaultend up
default paying for crewing the extra vehicle – a bus on the road for most of a ‘traffic day’ (
defaultearly
default 
defaultmorning to evening Monday-Friday
