default:
default(1) purchase 
defaultdearer, 
defaultnon-standard (
defaultie
default narrower
default) vehicles, which may reduce carrying capacity;
default(2) schedule less efficiently so that buses do not pass each other in restricted areas;
default(3) use minibuses, which have limited capacity, and may not satisfy travel demand.
